  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Freighter Engine Flare Modifier</span>.<br><br>A harmonic generation device converts the output of the freighter engines to <span class=\"name name-fuel\">A T L A S</span> frequencies, radiating a painfully crimson trail.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your freighter at the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Upgrade Control Terminal</span> on the <VAL_ON>bridge<>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">货船驱动信号器修改器</span>。<br><br>谐波发生装置将货船驱动器的输出转化为<span class=\"name name-fuel\">阿特拉斯</span>频率，从而散发出绯红如火的尾迹。<br><br>在<VAL_ON>舰桥<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升级组件控制终端</span>改变货船外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">貨船引擎火光改造器</span>。<br><br>諧波產生裝置將貨船引擎的輸出轉換為<span class=\"name name-fuel\">寰 宇</span> 頻率，散發出刺目的緋紅軌跡。<br><br>可在<VAL_ON>艦橋<>上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">升級控制終端站</span>裡變更你的貨船外觀。"
  },
